{"name": "mimesniff", "metadata": {"name": "mimesniff", "version": "1.1.1", "classifiers": ["Programming Language :: Python :: 3.4", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.5", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.6", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.7", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.8", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.9"], "home_page": "https://github.com/corona10/mimesniff", "license": "", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": [], "summary": "Pure python mimesniff implementation of https://mimesniff.spec.whatwg.org", "upload_time": 1603516315}, "documentation": ["# mimesniff\n\n```{image} https://travis-ci.org/corona10/mimesniff.svg?branch=master\n:target: https://travis-ci.org/corona10/mimesniff\n```\n\n```{image} https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/mimesniff.svg?style=flat\n:target: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/mimesniff\n```\n\nPure python mimesniff implementation of\n[https://mimesniff.spec.whatwg.org]\n\nAPI interface is similar with [API of python standard library]\n\n## Install\n\n```bash\npip install mimesniff\n```\n\n## Usage\n\n```python\nimport mimesniff\n\nres = mimesniff.what('sample.mp3')\nprint(res)\n# audio/mpeg\nwith open('sample.mp3', 'rb') as fin:\n    res = mimesniff.what(fin)\n    print(res)\n    # audio/mpeg\n\nwith open('sample.mp3', 'rb') as fin:\n    header = fin.read(512)\n    res = mimesniff.what(header)\n    print(res)\n    # audio/mpeg\n```\n\n[api of python standard library]: https://docs.python.org/3/library/sndhdr.html\n[https://mimesniff.spec.whatwg.org]: https://mimesniff.spec.whatwg.org\n"], "modules": [{"name": "mimesniff", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "mimesniff.what", "xref": {"fqname": "mimesniff.mimesniff.what", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "mimesniff.mimesniff", "documentation": ["Author: Dong-hee Na", "Contact: donghee.na92@gmail.com"], "functions": [{"name": "mimesniff.mimesniff.what", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "fin", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["mimesniff.what returns the MIME type of an HTTP response\nthrough mimesniffing\n\n```\nparam fin(str, io.BufferedIOBase, io.RawIOBase,  bytes)\n\n```\n\nFile(path, io.BufferedIOBase, io.RawIOBase, bytes) from which objects will\nbe detected\n\n```\nreturn\n\nstr that represent MIME type\n```\n\nreference: <https://mimesniff.spec.whatwg.org/>\n"]}, {"name": "mimesniff.mimesniff._", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "fin", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "mimesniff.mimesniff._", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "fin", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "mimesniff.mimesniff._", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "fin", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "mimesniff.mimesniff._is_ws", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "c", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "mimesniff.mimesniff._is_TT", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "c", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["https://mimesniff.spec.whatwg.org/#terminology."]}, {"name": "mimesniff.mimesniff._detect_content", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "h", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "mimesniff.mimesniff._match_html_types", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "h", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "first_non_ws", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "mimesniff.mimesniff._match_html_sig", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "h", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "sig", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "mimesniff.mimesniff._match_exact_sig_types", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "h", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "fir